ability0.name: Ability 1
ability0.text: {fontsize-10}You may have Aurra Sing deal 2 damage to target creature. If you don’t, Aurra Sing deals 1 damage to you.

ability1.name: Ability 2
ability1.text: {fontsize-10}Target player gets an emblem with “Whenever a nontoken creature you control leaves the battlefield, discard a card.”

ability2.name: Ability 3
ability2.text: {fontsize-10}Each player discards their hand and exiles all creatures they control. Each player’s life total becomes 1.
